tip.text: We had Gobi Manchurian, Chix 65 & Chix Briyani. It was authentically GOOD!! It was soo authentic tht you can even smell it before you even enter the rest. You will nvr believe tht you are in Houston!
It's AUNTHENTIC Thai food! Am soo happy to find this rest. True to the reviews online tht their foods are really gd. I had the Deep Fried Fish w/3 sauce. They serve BirdsEyeChillies in Texas!! O M G
Pad Thai Chicken Noodle is overcooked. There's no Bird's Eye Chilli with fish sauce - typical Thai chilli condiments. Seems like it's not an authentic Thai restaurant.
